      "id": "PopularPost39368",
      "post_content": "Companion to the ancient [Helm of Obedience](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Helm of Obedience) for an artifact block, without the quirk in wording that lets you combo with replacement effects to mill an entire library for ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol). The power of this card depends entirely on what kinds of decks your opponents are playing.",
      "posted_by": "Tanaka348",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost39368\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Companion to the ancient <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Helm of Obedience\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Helm of Obedience\">Helm of Obedience</a> for an artifact block, without the quirk in wording that lets you combo with replacement effects to mill an entire library for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/>. The power of this card depends entirely on what kinds of decks your opponents are playing.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '39368'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy19646\">Tanaka348</span>\r\n                                (12/4/2009 9:48:02 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\