      "id": "PopularPost213197",
      "post_content": "I use this in my [Glissa, The Traitor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glissa, The Traitor) EDH. Since I can get it back even if I find an artifact in their deck it basically lets me mill my opponent without fear of losing it and even stealing a bunch of their artifacts along the way. I have also used the [Jester's Cap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jester's Cap) and [Jester's Mask](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jester's Mask) to clear away some of their artifacts so I can just mill them without fear of losing my Thought Dissector to a signet or other small utility artifact, no if I'm Dissecting your Thoughts I'm going straight for the [Darksteel Colossus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Colossus) or [Wurmcoil Engine](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wurmcoil Engine) you were counting on for your win condition. Fun card in any deck that can bring it back repeatedly a la [Academy Ruins](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Academy Ruins) or the aforementioned legend.",
      "posted_by": "poprockmonster",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost213197\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I use this in my <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Glissa, The Traitor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glissa, The Traitor\">Glissa, The Traitor</a> EDH. Since I can get it back even if I find an artifact in their deck it basically lets me mill my opponent without fear of losing it and even stealing a bunch of their artifacts along the way. I have also used the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jester's Cap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jester's Cap\">Jester's Cap</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jester's Mask\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jester's Mask\">Jester's Mask</a> to clear away some of their artifacts so I can just mill them without fear of losing my Thought Dissector to a signet or other small utility artifact, no if I'm Dissecting your Thoughts I'm going straight for the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Darksteel Colossus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Colossus\">Darksteel Colossus</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wurmcoil Engine\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wurmcoil Engine\">Wurmcoil Engine</a> you were counting on for your win condition. Fun card in any deck that can bring it back repeatedly a la <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Academy Ruins\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Academy Ruins\">Academy Ruins</a> or the aforementioned legend.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"Hand